author: Lalph-Rauren
body: With such a negative attitude there are other possibilities as well, like a meteorite hitting the earth wiping us all out. Or another world war where we reach full armageddon.   Just try to look at yourself as in individual and think, what can I do in this situation. Not even considering $KENDU, just as a whole in life.  Focus on growth, focus on output, focus on the positives. That’s what counts in my opinion. Don’t yap about “sell-pressure” when the market is going sideways for weeks.  Complaining gets you nowhere in life.  Taking action and going forward will.  May I ask, why do you think we are going to 0?
